{"tid":1457024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽」「極重要」組織聽日活動+宣傳","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:35.000Z","uid":37753,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e5681f7eb47e52f4113af22e62a92bd262d3d5","tid":1457024,"uid":37753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"去到呢一刻，唔需要再去嘈留/走。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現場仲留低既手足自己判斷，大家只需要updata相關交通資訊</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ukb4Bzj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUkb4Bzj.jpg&h=fd1f9c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日的而且確成功<span style=\"color: red;\">高度影響</span>機場運動<br />\n亦話已經話左比政府聽我地有足夠既<span style=\"color: red;\">動員同輿論能力</span>，可以短時間內組織到大型集會<br />\n<br />\n但我地深深知道香港人係<span style=\"color: red;\">善忘</span>，如果冇持續推動整體活動，會令運動再次<span style=\"color: red;\">冷卻</span> ，佔領機場係依加既新方向，必須要令佢<span style=\"color: red;\">持續</span><br />\n<br />\n必須注意有巴絲提出，過去發生過好多次大型天災令到機場停止運作，<span style=\"color: red;\">機管局係有足夠能力去處理善後工作</span>，如果我地唔將呢個方向持續<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府表示：你咁樣係唔會令到我驚架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以所以，我懇求今日出左黎既手足<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日繼續出黎</span></span><br />\n我地需要既係持續性，而唔係單次既滿足感<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 我覺得呢一刻唔走都唔會有咩危險 <br />\n但相對上保留體力會唔會係比較明智既做法呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZY6PYJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZY6PYJ.jpg&h=029790d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望現場睇到post既手足思考一下"},{"pid":"c20e930cf33676d5140122733b1eda12b13fa3c8","tid":1457024,"uid":37753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a26a02f2740f8c70c040ebd4b379b9b596734bc1","tid":1457024,"uid":99384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"160c1274509c060c68892b3c71220610d2f